"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"President Donald Trump said the operation eliminated a very active terrorist, Abu-Bilal al-Minuki. Trump also wants China and Taiwan to calm down tensions over Taiwan.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump on Terrorist and Taiwan\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente Donald Trump dijo que la operaci\u00f3n elimin\u00f3 a un terrorista muy activo, Abu-Bilal al-Minuki. Trump tambi\u00e9n quiere que China y Taiw\u00e1n calmen las tensiones sobre Taiw\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Trump sobre Terrorista y Taiw\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"President Trump announced a truce last month, but Israel and Hezbollah have continued to exchange fire since then.\",            \"english_title\": \"Truce and Conflict\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente Trump anunci\u00f3 una tregua el mes pasado, pero Israel y Hezbollah han continuado intercambiando disparos desde entonces.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tregua y Conflicto\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Charges could come soon in a case focused on Cuba's downing of two planes in 1996.\",            \"english_title\": \"Cuba Plane Case\",            \"translated_version\": \"Podr\u00edan llegar cargos pronto en un caso centrado en el derribo de dos aviones por Cuba en 1996.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Caso de Aviones en Cuba\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"There were many ceremonies but no trade breakthroughs after a two-day visit.\",            \"english_title\": \"No Trade Breakthroughs\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hubo muchas ceremonias pero no avances comerciales despu\u00e9s de una visita de dos d\u00edas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Sin Avances Comerciales\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Africa's top health agency says around 246 cases have been reported, and a case has also been reported in Uganda.\",            \"english_title\": \"Health Cases in Africa\",            \"translated_version\": \"La principal agencia de salud de \u00c1frica dice que se han reportado alrededor de 246 casos, y tambi\u00e9n se ha reportado un caso en Uganda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Casos de Salud en \u00c1frica\"        }    ]}"